1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
♪By your side once♪

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,086
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,087 --> 00:00:46,182
=Episode 10=

12
00:00:46,740 --> 00:00:47,859
Ministers, I've received

13
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:49,539
word of unrest beyond our borders.

14
00:00:49,540 --> 00:00:51,260
I've decided to reinforce the frontier.

15
00:00:51,300 --> 00:00:52,900
Sun Gong, Minister of War,

16
00:00:53,020 --> 00:00:55,379
you're currently
overseeing treasury allocations.

17
00:00:55,380 --> 00:00:57,259
Release fifty million
taels of silver at once

18
00:00:57,260 --> 00:00:58,939
to purchase arms and warhorses,

19
00:00:58,940 --> 00:01:00,379
and reinforce the frontier.

20
00:01:00,380 --> 00:01:01,899
Your Majesty, this matter

21
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:03,099
is of great importance.

22
00:01:03,100 --> 00:01:04,259
It must not be taken lightly.

23
00:01:04,260 --> 00:01:05,699
Whether there is truly unrest

24
00:01:05,700 --> 00:01:07,219
is still unclear.

25
00:01:07,220 --> 00:01:08,539
Yet Your Majesty now proposes

26
00:01:08,540 --> 00:01:10,299
to spend tens of millions of taels

27
00:01:10,300 --> 00:01:11,539
raising troops and horses,

28
00:01:11,540 --> 00:01:12,939
without even an imperial edict.

29
00:01:12,940 --> 00:01:14,980
Isn't that somewhat rash?

30
00:01:15,380 --> 00:01:17,340
My verbal decree is
itself an imperial edict.

31
00:01:17,820 --> 00:01:20,340
Do my ministers
think I am being frivolous?

32
00:01:26,500 --> 00:01:28,700
I don't find it frivolous at all.

33
00:01:28,860 --> 00:01:31,579
Not only should troops
be sent to the frontier,

34
00:01:31,580 --> 00:01:33,299
the imperial guards within the capital

35
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:34,579
should also be redeployed.

36
00:01:34,580 --> 00:01:35,819
Your Highness,

37
00:01:35,820 --> 00:01:37,379
with all due respect,

38
00:01:37,380 --> 00:01:39,339
but if you continue
to indulge His Majesty,

39
00:01:39,340 --> 00:01:41,779
it may bring unrest upon the realm.

40
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:42,900
Sun Gong,

41
00:01:43,460 --> 00:01:45,100
within this court,

42
00:01:45,300 --> 00:01:48,139
even if His Majesty stood
beside the late emperor,

43
00:01:48,140 --> 00:01:51,179
they would be ruler
and subject before father and son.

44
00:01:51,180 --> 00:01:52,300
Sun Gong,

45
00:01:53,100 --> 00:01:54,580
do you understand?

46
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:57,620
Your Highness, forgive me.

47
00:01:57,660 --> 00:01:58,779
Your Majesty, forgive me.

48
00:01:58,780 --> 00:02:00,299
But I need an imperial edict

49
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:02,419
to relay orders
through the chain of command.

50
00:02:02,420 --> 00:02:03,779
Without a written edict,

51
00:02:03,780 --> 00:02:05,619
it can't be carried out at every level.

52
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:06,819
The situation is urgent.

53
00:02:06,820 --> 00:02:09,459
Have the Directorate
of Ceremonial draft the edict at once.

54
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:11,939
The Directorate should indeed
draft an edict for Your Majesty.

55
00:02:11,940 --> 00:02:12,859
However,

56
00:02:12,860 --> 00:02:14,499
I do believe

57
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:17,660
that Minister Sun makes a valid point.

58
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:19,660
Your Majesty should reconsider.

59
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:22,019
This matter is extremely urgent.

60
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:23,460
What is there to reconsider?

61
00:02:23,860 --> 00:02:25,220
Let the Directorate

62
00:02:25,260 --> 00:02:26,580
draft the edict at once.

63
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:29,539
The Directorate will certainly do
all it can to assist Your Majesty.

64
00:02:29,540 --> 00:02:30,660
It's just that...

65
00:02:31,300 --> 00:02:35,099
the edict requires the Directorate's
seal before it can be enforced.

66
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:36,699
With layers of review,

67
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:38,259
it may take some time.

68
00:02:38,260 --> 00:02:41,300
Your Majesty, please wait a few days.

69
00:02:55,420 --> 00:02:56,540
Fine.

70
00:02:56,580 --> 00:02:58,900
Then we'll do as you say, Jia Yi.

71
00:02:59,340 --> 00:03:01,339
After all, my role as the Emperor

72
00:03:01,340 --> 00:03:03,060
is nothing but a game.

73
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:13,420
We might as well watch the dancing.

74
00:03:26,940 --> 00:03:28,380
Gentlemen,

75
00:03:30,060 --> 00:03:31,620
you are dismissed.

76
00:03:37,180 --> 00:03:38,886
What happened today was far too obvious.

77
00:03:38,887 --> 00:03:40,767
The Grand Princess will grow suspicious.

78
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:42,460
We can't worry about that now.

79
00:03:44,450 --> 00:03:47,403
Chu Wuju rarely
goes along with Chu Ying.

80
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:50,474
Yet today, she not only
agreed to his absurd request,

81
00:03:50,475 --> 00:03:52,875
she even wants to send
her guards beyond the pass.

82
00:03:53,260 --> 00:03:55,140
I'm afraid she has other motives.

83
00:03:56,300 --> 00:03:57,940
Whatever her intentions,

84
00:03:58,140 --> 00:03:59,660
we'll move faster.

85
00:03:59,740 --> 00:04:01,180
End this quickly.

86
00:04:01,580 --> 00:04:02,259
In half a month,

87
00:04:02,260 --> 00:04:03,859
the foreign forces will arrive.

88
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:05,819
I'll personally
lead troops to the frontier

89
00:04:05,820 --> 00:04:07,059
and let them in.

90
00:04:07,060 --> 00:04:08,899
A unit of imperial guards
within the capital

91
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,339
was once part of the Xiao Army.

92
00:04:10,340 --> 00:04:11,659
They'll answer to you, Uncle,

93
00:04:11,660 --> 00:04:13,339
and swear loyalty unto death.

94
00:04:13,340 --> 00:04:15,139
We'll strike from within and without

95
00:04:15,140 --> 00:04:17,580
and wipe out the entire Chu dynasty.

96
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:20,419
If war breaks out

97
00:04:20,420 --> 00:04:21,459
at the frontier,

98
00:04:21,460 --> 00:04:22,339
Father and Mother...

99
00:04:22,340 --> 00:04:23,340
Silence!

100
00:04:23,940 --> 00:04:26,139
I'm your elder brother.

101
00:04:26,140 --> 00:04:27,940
And he is your uncle.

102
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:31,420
Xiao Man.

103
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:35,499
If I hadn't stopped you by force today,

104
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:38,420
would you have sided
with that young emperor?

105
00:04:45,300 --> 00:04:46,500
Take this.

106
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:53,860
Come to me
every three days for the antidote.

107
00:04:54,340 --> 00:04:56,660
Your brother and I
have already taken it.

108
00:04:57,060 --> 00:04:59,140
I pitied you for being young.

109
00:04:59,420 --> 00:05:02,220
But now, you are already an adult.

110
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:04,420
Swallow it.

111
00:05:10,940 --> 00:05:12,259
War is approaching.

112
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:14,220
There is no room for your hesitation.

113
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:17,899
Don't let your childish
affections ruin the revenge

114
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:21,020
I've planned for over a decade.

115
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:25,660
I have a task for you.

116
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:27,460
Go to the Imperial Study.

117
00:05:27,780 --> 00:05:29,019
Steal the roster of the officials

118
00:05:29,020 --> 00:05:32,140
who fanned the flames
of the Zhen clan's wrongful case.

119
00:05:32,340 --> 00:05:33,980
When we make our move,

120
00:05:34,020 --> 00:05:35,619
I want them to taste

121
00:05:35,620 --> 00:05:37,980
what it means
to lose their families and homes.

122
00:05:39,500 --> 00:05:41,860
Perhaps Father and Mother
wouldn't have wanted this.

123
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:44,179
They were kind people.

124
00:05:44,180 --> 00:05:46,580
They would never wish
to implicate the innocent.

125
00:05:47,620 --> 00:05:48,979
If their spirits watch from above,

126
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:51,299
they'd want you
to let go of your hatred, Uncle.

127
00:05:51,300 --> 00:05:52,539
And find some happiness.

128
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:53,660
Uncle...

129
00:05:56,180 --> 00:05:57,939
War is fast approaching.

130
00:05:57,940 --> 00:06:00,380
Put away
that soft-hearted mercy of yours.

131
00:06:00,420 --> 00:06:02,340
People like us...

132
00:06:03,860 --> 00:06:06,019
have no right to kindness.

133
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:08,420
And even less right to happiness!

134
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:13,860
Since we've already come this far,

135
00:06:14,140 --> 00:06:17,579
even if I'm bound
for the depths of hell,

136
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:20,300
I'll drag them down with me!

137
00:06:30,100 --> 00:06:31,540
For the sake of vengeance,

138
00:06:31,860 --> 00:06:34,619
I cast aside life and death long ago.

139
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:35,740
Let alone

140
00:06:35,940 --> 00:06:38,540
those strangers who mean nothing to me.

141
00:06:39,860 --> 00:06:40,980
Mu Jun.

142
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:43,380
Mu Yu.

143
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:48,060
Don't forget

144
00:06:48,700 --> 00:06:52,380
why I raised the two of you.

145
00:06:54,780 --> 00:06:58,259
Your parents were such good people.

146
00:06:58,260 --> 00:07:01,340
How can you bear
to let them die in vain?

147
00:07:15,220 --> 00:07:16,340
Xiao Man,

148
00:07:17,860 --> 00:07:19,580
don't resent me.

149
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:22,380
This isn't what I wanted either.

150
00:07:23,660 --> 00:07:25,460
(I don't hate you, Uncle.)

151
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:28,340
(I don't hate you, Uncle.)

152
00:07:30,550 --> 00:07:31,899
(Yangxin Hall)

153
00:07:31,900 --> 00:07:33,020
Your Majesty.

154
00:07:35,420 --> 00:07:37,379
After court was dismissed,

155
00:07:37,380 --> 00:07:40,060
Sun Gong and Jia Yi met again
in the private chamber at Yanbo Parlor.

156
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:43,020
Where's Xiao Man?

157
00:07:44,180 --> 00:07:45,300
He was there too.

158
00:07:46,425 --> 00:07:51,745
(Yangxin Hall)

159
00:08:38,220 --> 00:08:39,299
Are you hurt?

160
00:08:39,300 --> 00:08:40,140
Here.

161
00:08:40,620 --> 00:08:41,979
I only meant to kick the door open.

162
00:08:41,980 --> 00:08:43,620
I didn't know you were behind it.

163
00:08:45,820 --> 00:08:46,899
I am unharmed.

164
00:08:46,900 --> 00:08:48,460
Thank you for your concern.

165
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:52,940
I didn't see you just now.

166
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:58,740
I shouldn't have
entered the Imperial Study.

167
00:08:58,860 --> 00:09:00,580
I beg Your Majesty's forgiveness.

168
00:09:24,562 --> 00:09:27,770
(Yangxin Hall)

169
00:09:51,740 --> 00:09:52,980
(Do you trust me?)

170
00:09:53,260 --> 00:09:54,540
(I trust you.)

171
00:09:58,940 --> 00:10:00,060
(Xiao Man,)

172
00:10:00,260 --> 00:10:01,579
(out of the entire world,)

173
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:03,260
(the only person I trust)

174
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:04,860
(is you.)

175
00:10:12,700 --> 00:10:13,619
Eunuch Xiao Man,

176
00:10:13,620 --> 00:10:15,500
His Majesty summons you.

177
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,820
(Xiao Man,)

178
00:11:15,300 --> 00:11:16,740
(I'm deeply troubled.)

179
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:19,900
(I can clearly feel your sincerity,)

180
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:23,780
(but you're also helping Jia Yi
in his plot to seize power.)

181
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:26,660
(What are you really thinking?)

182
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:33,780
Serve the meal.

183
00:11:38,540 --> 00:11:39,660
Your Majesty,

184
00:11:39,740 --> 00:11:40,860
please dine.

185
00:11:48,140 --> 00:11:49,420
(Does it hurt?)

186
00:11:54,140 --> 00:11:55,940
(I never meant to hurt you.)

187
00:11:56,660 --> 00:11:58,940
(But what were you doing
in the Imperial Study?)

188
00:11:59,540 --> 00:12:01,460
(What are you trying to do?)

189
00:12:02,740 --> 00:12:04,580
(You owe me an explanation.)

190
00:12:06,780 --> 00:12:08,900
(Are you not
the same person I once knew?)

191
00:12:10,860 --> 00:12:13,220
(I don't even know how to face you now.)

192
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:18,340
Your Majesty, please dine.

193
00:12:22,180 --> 00:12:23,260
Take it away.
